  «text (2160,2340) 1 7 0 0x1000000 -1 -1 "ď»ż*** user input parameters ***\n.param Rload=10K\n.param Vdd=5\n.param Vss=-5\n*** .ac analysis setup ***\n.param FirstFreq=1m\n.param LastFreq=1G\n.param PtsPerDecade=100"»
  «text (2195,320) 1 7 0 0x1000000 -1 -1 "ď»ż; simulation\n.ac dec PtsPerDecade FirstFreq LastFreq\n.plot V(out)\n.abscissa Frequency\n\n; measurement\n.func dB(x) 20*log10(abs(x))\n.meas |AVOL| find abs(V(OUT)) at FirstFreq\n.meas AVOL-dB find dB(V(OUT)) at FirstFreq\n.meas GBW find Frequency when abs(V(OUT))=1"»
